            ด้วย</span></font><a href="javascript:na_open_window('win', 'ex3.htm#ิอุเบกขา', 0, 0, 1250, 300, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1)"><span style="font-size:16pt;"><font face="Leelawadee"><b>อุเบกขา</b></font></span></a><span style="font-size:16pt;"><font face="Leelawadee"><b> 
